title: Apartment for Rent
description: This 1-bedroom apartment is located in the Vreewijk neighborhood of Rotterdam. It offers a convenient location with nearby amenities such as schools, supermarkets, and bus stops. The apartment is part of the Startmotor project and is available for a minimum rental period of 1 year. The rent price is €755 per month (excluding service costs of €212 per month). The apartment is 31m² in size and is available for immediate occupancy. The security deposit is €1,000. For more information and to schedule viewings, please visit the provided link.

importantInformation.viewings: Viewings can be scheduled through the provided link.
